did.unittitle:
Song lists and personnel
                     for all recordings in the Redwood Canyon Ramblers Archive,

 circa 2013

scopecontent.p:
Each event (except
SR54
) is described in this document. Brian Miksis compiled the information based on documentation that accompanied the recordings, his own research, observations while digitizing the recordings, and guidance from Neil Rosenberg (e.g., when the pitch needed adjustment to restore the audio quality). This document includes the names of the musicians, instruments played, the source recording history, the name and address of the recording location, and technical metadata regarding digitization.
